cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.HC 

This paper is about image annotation for semantic segmentation, which is a topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of crowdsourcing and weakly-supervised learning, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also proposes a method for inpainting block-annotated images, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
